title: 🤑🤑FULL SIZE KITCHEN + ALL BILLS PAID! COME STAY AWHILE!
posting_body: ['Budget Suites invites you to relax and unwind in your own personal apartment whether you are a family relocating to a new city, a business traveler, vacationer, or just making a new start here in North Dallas.', 'Our apartments are spacious, comfortable and equally affordable for any budget.', 'Our properties are designed to serve you with many amenities including all utilities paid, full sized kitchens & appliances, pools & spas, laundry facilities with courtesy patrol, cable with premium channels including Showtime & ESPN and much more.', 'Budget Suites has the conveniences of a hotel, with all the comforts of home.', 'We welcome you to your new home.', 'At every Budget Suites you will find the same valuable services at a price you can value just as much.', 'Our famous budget prices include:', '• Fully Furnished Apartments', '• All Utilities paid', '• Cable TV', '• Free Local Calls and Voicemail', '• Full Sized Kitchens', '• Full Sized Appliances', '• On-Site laundry Facilities', '• Offices Open 7 Days A Week', '• Beautiful Pool', 'And Spas', '• Onsite Maintenance', '• Plenty of Parking', '• Courtesy Patrol', 'Available upgrades to your apartment include:', '• Deluxe Flooring', '• Flat Screen HD TV', '• Microwave', 'Weekly rates start as low as $289(+tax), deposit is required at check-in with first payment.', 'No credit check is required.', 'No application fee.', 'No lease.', 'Move in on the same day!', 'Budget Suites of America.', 'Come live a while.']
